Computer Architecture (Assembly Linux Nasm)
============

Work done in Linux ASSEMBLY 486. It calculates sine, cosine, tangent, cotangent, arcsine, arccosine, arctangent and arccotangent. Based on Taylor series.

Work authors:

Davide Barruncho
